        <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-ink-900 dark:text-white">fine-tuned + retrieval</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-ink-700 dark:text-ink-300">82.6%</td><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-mono text-ink-500">+17.4 <span class="text-ink-500">learned</span></td></tr>
